description.content:
Hello Fiverr Community,


Welcome to ICIEOS Pvt Ltd!


We are a dynamic team consist of 15 professionals with expertise in software engineering, UI/UX designing, BA and QA. We have experience in the IT industry for more than 5 years in website development and web/ mobile application development. We design websites from scratch for individuals, small businesses and also for corporate sector.


Our Expertise:


We have experience in various industries including e-commerce, e-learning, banking, hospitality, booking platforms, and government projects. Whether it is a simple website or a complex solution like cloud based ERP system our team has the potential to deliver it.



What is our tech stack?


Front-end Development

  • React JS
  • Angular
  • Vue.js
  • CSS/SCSS, HTML, JavaScript


Mobile Development

  • React Native
  • Flutter
  • Kotlin
  • Swift


Backend Development

  • Java - Spring Boot
  • NodeJS - Express
  • PHP - Laravel
  • Python - Django


Databases

  • MYSQL, PostgreSQL
  • MongoDB
  • Firebase


Other

  • Power BI for dashboard design
  • Figma
  • Adobe XD


Styling


  • Tailwind CSS
  • Material-UI
  • Ant Design
  • Framer Motion


We are here to help you create a website that exceeds your expectations. Contact us today for a free consultation!
